---
title: Herby Yogurt Marinated Turkey with Roasted Zucchini Sticks and Sweet Potato Mash
description: Tender turkey, sweet potatoes, zucchini, and a creamy herby yogurt dip come together in the ultimate comfort dinner. Easy, fast and packed with flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/herby-yogurt-marinated-turkey-71d5428e.jpg
